<HEADLINE>
FT  18 OCT 94 / World News in Brief: Bomb kills Russian reporter
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A suitcase bomb killed investigative reporter Dmitry Kholodov and destroyed
the newsroom of Moskovsky Komsomolets, a popular Moscow newspaper that had
crusaded against the Russian mafia.
</TEXT>
